Name: Altair
Notes:
Atair, Al Nesr Al Tair, Vulture Volans;[1] 12th brightest star; nearby; has 
two optical components; δ Sct variable, Δ*V* = 0.004m, *P* = 0.06342 d

Notes:

suspected variable
